(12, 'Book Seven of Esme\'s Ladies'),
(15, 'As someone who hates prophecy, Lydan seems an unlikely guardian of the Prophetic Vaults of Yu\'ul. But it was prophecied that someone matching her description would someday save Yu\'ul from its doom. The Elders don\'t take such things lightly. But what, Lyda'),
(16, '\"The best beach-book I\'ve ever read\" \"Easy and fun without being vapid\"'),
