(21, 'Lowry\'s comedic genius shines through every moment of her memoir. Told with clear eyes and biting wit, the anecdotes of each chapter bring to life a world of eccentric academics. The literarily-inclinded daughter of a physicist  and an epidemiologist, Low'),
